txt.en: A group of mischevious young hobbits organizes a yearly secret raid of Farmer Maggot's fields, seeking to snatch wild mushrooms that grow among the grain...and each year Farmer Maggot sets his dogs loose in the field to chase them off. Can you prove your worth as a veteran mushroom-hunter?
You have proven yourself a fine mushroom-hunter. The hobbit-youths look up to you in reverence and awe, as you nimbly avoid the pursuit of Maggot's dogs.
